    {
        "content": "<p>Probably this page would be most useful to link to, since it shows the build results that run right before bors merges commits into <code>master</code>: <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/actions/workflows/bors.yml\">https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/actions/workflows/bors.yml</a></p>",
